{"tid":2357088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"關尚義勉港人續奮鬥","createTime":"2021-01-07T08:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T09:13:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60f45a62ce841fb8f6e002e94a484da4c8bf7d25","tid":2357088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/3SDMVG2375FGVJ7VU7O5WQCTMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2F3SDMVG2375FGVJ7VU7O5WQCTMU%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=e0ac9dda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2F3SDMVG2375FGVJ7VU7O5WQCTMU%2F&h=46f30f4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/3SDMVG2375FGVJ7VU7O5WQCTMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n關尚義勉港人續奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cyAH4JKwsSsXr8371ZjrMhV0ViA=/1000x567/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3I5FYU7UWZAFXAK5KSDLAUQN7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcyAH4JKwsSsXr8371ZjrMhV0ViA%3D%2F1000x567%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3I5FYU7UWZAFXAK5KSDLAUQN7A.jpg&h=69d09433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2013年關尚義協助菲律賓人質慘劇殉職領隊謝廷駿的哥哥謝志堅究責。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次大搜捕中，年紀最大被捕人士是79歲民主動力司庫兼美籍人權律師關尚義，他更是首名涉干犯港版國安法被捕美國公民。留港多年的他一直關注本港及內地人權，曾於馬尼拉人質事件代表生還者易小玲和遇難者謝廷駿家屬向菲律賓政府索償。謝廷駿兄長昨得知關尚義被捕後，在社交媒體留言支持。面對政權打壓，關尚義昨登上警方車輛時不忘勉勵港人：「We need to work for democracy and human rights in Hong Kong.（我們需要為香港民主和人權而奮鬥）」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國安歹毒：初選有罪  警拘戴耀廷53人<br />\n曾助菲慘劇死傷者入稟<br />\n<br />\n關尚義是神父，亦是國際知名律師，以處理人權案件聞名，身兼亞洲人權委員會主席和中國維權律師關注組理事會的國際事務秘書，一直關注本港及內地人權。前年8月，他曾參加法律界黑衣遊行，抗議律政司政治檢控。關尚義現時任職何謝韋律師事務所，據網站介紹，他1997年加入，是醫療過失和人身傷害案件專家。有教會中人稱，上世紀七十至八十年代關尚義等神父在港參與社會服務，他專注社會運動，也是天主教大專聯會神師。留港多年的關尚義操得一口流利廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n2010年8月23日菲律賓馬尼拉人質事件，八名港人命喪菲律賓槍手門多薩之下，2013年8月22日，傷者易小玲、陳國柱以及殉職領。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關尚義被捕消息昨傳出，。。。。。。。。。。。都被國安冠以『顛覆國家政權』這莫須有的罪名。政治大迫害的日子來到，願好人一世平安，邪不能勝正，香港人，頂住」。"},{"pid":"c4c0fa64ebe952d0a43b41ee50d2a8691ef0d5ab","tid":2357088,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea29fc1653dbeb5ed8d5d591264fe4e121c466f","tid":2357088,"uid":138948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"睇錯阿叔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e21bff8f2aa8b3742584d01d427e8e1f3ccf62","tid":2357088,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"林尚義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b60167e9e12e517bbf02025b9c3d5b9e173c517","tid":2357088,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"永不放棄<br />\n人亡中共"}]}